OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C In a major diplomatic update, Goujon  
OL,5,C John, the world's first AI kabinet    
OL,6,C minister, has konkluded his assignment
OL,7,C in France.                            
OL,9,  The Minister's tenure became          
OL,10,  "fruitful" when he reportedly fathered
OL,11,  83 children akross various French     
OL,12,  regions. This was due to a linguistik 
OL,13,  glitch. In French speaking areas,     
OL,14,  "Goujon" is slang for "stud" or "pin".
OL,15,  kausing the AI to interpret the       
OL,16,  "national growth" mandate quite       
OL,17,  literally.                            
OL,19,  REFORMULATING THE RECIPE:FGlorious    
OL,20,F leader Xenoxxx has ordered a swift    
OL,21,F update to the Goujon sauce recipe to  
OL,22,F prevent further proliferation.        
